ts than any of our competitors great brands at great value translate into great deals for our customerswe are a publicly traded company operating more than  stores in  states and puerto rico over the past  years we have added more than  stores each year and are on our way to  stores our corporate campus is located in florence new jersey just minutes from metrophiladelphia bucolic bucks county pennsylvania and trendy princeton new jersey in addition we have buying offices in the heart of the fashion districts of los angeles and new york cityas well as distribution centers in new jersey and californiaat the center of our success are the over  associates that call burlington stores “home” each associate contributes to our growth by driving results through teamwork open and honest communications and mutual respect we work together have fun together and celebrate our successes togetherwe also operate cohoes fashions super baby depot mjm designer shoes and burlington shoes stores  contact headquarters route  burlington nj  united states culture our burlingtonwhen you first come to work at burlington you’re not just joining a company you’re becoming part of a family and there are things we experience within this family that are unique to working at burlington the elements of our culture set burlington apart from the competition our burlington captures those attributes that are representative of our unique company culture it represents the entire associate experience at our company touching on those things beyond pay or benefitswe are an offprice retailerwe deliver great values to our customers every day our teams stay focused on executing the offprice model by ensuring we have the right product in the right stores at the right time for our customerswe live by our core valueswe drive resultsour fastpaced work place and culture allow us to continuously evolve the offprice model we hold ourselves and each other accountable for our business success and have a shared sense of ownership to achieve our company goalswe trust  respect each otherthe way we do business is equally as important as the results we achieve we have a sharedcommitment to conduct business ethically and treat customers business partnersand each other with trust and respectwe build teams  partnershipsthrough collaborative teamwork we solve complex business challenges togetherwe believe everyone matterswe listen to the individual viewpoints of our diverse workforce through open and honestcommunication our associates come from diverse backgrounds and offer unique perspectives onaccomplishing our goals everyone’s contribution is valuedwe win togetherwe recognize those who make a difference great performance leads to exciting careeropportunities so as we grow you do too at burlington we are continually expanding our learning and recognition programs to ensure that our associates feel rewarded and grow in their careers whether it’s an online ecourse one of our popular lunch  learn events or an instructorled classroom session we are dedicated to providing our associates with the experiences materials and training needed to have a long and successful careerwe are a caring companywe have a caring work environment and the generosity of our associates and customershelps to improve the communities we live and work in and beyond we know we can make the greatest impact by supporting causes that affect the lives of our associates customers and their families our charitable partnerships include the warm coats  warm hearts drive leukemia and lymphoma society donorschooseorg and womenheart the national coalition for women with heart disease burlington and our associates have raised millions for organizations that provide support to those in need recommended jobs for you see all jobs burlington skip to main content free shipping   free instore returns  this action will open a popup window find a store shop gift cards read our blog shop plus size new arrivals shop summer dresses for less s